    <stitle>ANTILOCK BRAKES/TRACTION CONTROL: BENDIX - PRINCIPLES, OPERATION AND SERVICE - INSTALL - SENSOR RETAINERS
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="0">
        <title>SENSOR RETAINERS</title>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Front Axle Retainer</title>
            <para>Install the front sensor retainer by pushing it into the sensor bushing from the axle side until the
                retainer tongues are against the sensor bushing.
            </para>
        </svcsubproc>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Rear Axle Retainer</title>
            <para>Install the rear sensor retainer by pushing it into the sensor mounting block from the axle side until
                the retainer tongues are against the sensor mounting block.
            </para>
        </svcsubproc>
    </svcproc>
